      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example excels mechanically, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous response and the limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power delivery. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension remains taut, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback these chassis are known for. While it shows honest patina consistent with its age, the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust and ready for spirited use.",
